Class OperationSyncApiInterface

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ApiInterface

    public class OperationSyncApiInterface
extends com.vmware.vapi.internal.bindings.ApiInterfaceSkeleton
    Implementation of ApiInterfaceSkeleton which adapts API service implementation (class that implements the generated OperationSyncProvider interface).

    This adapter expects synchronous API service implementation.
